---
import LocationIcon from "../../icons/LocationIcon.astro";
import ToolIcon from "../../icons/ToolIcon.astro";
---

<section
    id="sobre-mi"
    class="relative bg-[#050B14] min-h-screen flex items-center overflow-hidden"
>
    <!-- Subtle dark background glow -->
    <div
        class="absolute top-[-20%] left-[-10%] w-[50%] h-[50%] rounded-full bg-blue-900/10 blur-[120px] pointer-events-none"
    >
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-350 w-full mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8 lg:px-12">
        <div
            class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center justify-between lg:gap-12"
        >
            <!-- Left Content -->
            <div
                class="w-full flex flex-col items-center justify-center z-10 reveal opacity-0 translate-y-10 transition-all duration-1000 ease-out"
            >
                <!-- Badge -->
                <div
                    class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-slate-800/60 border border-slate-700/50 backdrop-blur-sm mb-10"
                >
                    <ToolIcon />
                    <span
                        class="text-[11px] font-bold tracking-[0.15em] text-slate-300 uppercase mt-px"
                        >Servicios</span
                    >
                </div>

                <!-- Heading -->
                <h1
                    class="text-[2.75rem] text-center sm:text-6xl lg:text-[5.5rem] font-bold text-white tracking-tight leading-[1.05] mb-8"
                >
                    Servicios de desarrollo web
                    <span
                        class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-linear-to-r from-[#22b2ff] to-[#4970ff] inline-block my-2"
                        >especializado en obtener clientes</span
                    >
                </h1>

                <!-- Description -->
                <p
                    class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-slate-400 text-center leading-relaxed mb-12"
                >
                    Ayudo a negocios y profesionales a tener una web más clara,
                    más profesional y mejor enfocada en captar oportunidades. Mi
                    trabajo no consiste solo en desarrollar páginas: consiste en
                    construir una web que represente bien tu negocio.
                </p>

                <!-- Buttons -->
                <div
                    class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center gap-4 mb-16 w-full sm:w-auto"
                >
                    <a
                        href="/#contacto"
                        class="w-full sm:w-auto inline-flex justify-center items-center px-8 py-4 rounded-full bg-[#15b1ff] hover:bg-blue-500 text-white font-medium text-lg transition-transform hover:scale-105 duration-300 shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(21,177,255,0.3)]"
                    >
                        Contacte ahora
                    </a>
                    <a
                        href="#paquetes-web"
                        class="w-full sm:w-auto inline-flex justify-center items-center px-8 py-4 rounded-full bg-[#1e2532] hover:bg-[#2a3343] text-white font-medium text-lg transition-transform hover:scale-105 duration-300"
                    >
                        Ver servicios
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
